NULinks is a chrome extension and website to enable Northeastern students to quickly access Northeastern University websites.

Activate the extension by typing "nu" and then space or tab into the browser's address bar. Once activated, you can quickly search for any of the Northeastern sites, such as Blackboard, Husky Mail, NUCareers, NU Dining, XFINITY On-Campus, Student Employment, PaperCut and many more.

Clicking on the extension's icon or activating the extension and then immediately  pressing enter without searching for anything will bring you to the extension's detailed search page where you can scroll through the results and see longer descriptions.

NULinks is unofficial and run by students. Suggest improvements at the NULinks GitHub: https://github.com/kj800x/nulinks
